snippet: Jose Quintana allowed two hits in eight innings and Kevin Youkilis homered as Chicago prevailed in a series between division leaders.
abstract: MLB Roundup; Chicago White Sox defeat Texas Rangers, 2-1, to complete a three-game sweep; other results noted.
